                   <p>You grant to HiTeck Education  a revocable, non-transferable, royalty free, international license to display on and distribute from HiTeck Education  Website Content that You provide to HiTeck Education  through the Network Service for the limited purposes of promoting You to Advertisers, subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement and the Advertiser’s Advertiser Service Agreement. The right to display such Content sub-licensable by HiTeck Education to Your Advertisers, for the limited purpose of advertising that You are a member of Advertiser’s Program. Your Advertisers may not distribute and/or sublicense Your Content unless authorized by Your written permission. HiTeck Education and sub-licensees shall not otherwise copy nor modify, in any way, any Content that You have made available through the Network Service pursuant to the foregoing license. HiTeck Education and the sub-licensees may not remove or alter any copyright or trademark notices.</p>
