                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">10.Affiliates Information e.g. email, performance statistics.</h2>
                <p class="mt-2">The Affiliate consents to the publication of the Affiliate’s name and web address etc on the HiTeck Education website and to HiTeck Education sending newsletters etc to the Affiliate’s e-mail address and using the information given by the Affiliate for marketing purposes. The Affiliate confirms that in order to enable HiTeck Education to improve and/or to promote or market the service, HiTeck Education may produce statistics or summaries relating to the use of the service.</p>
                <p class="mt-2">HiTeck Education may contact the Affiliate by email, telephone or post for feedback relating to the service including any ways in which it might be improved both for the network and for the individual Affiliate.</p>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">11.Legal Age.</h2>
                <p class="mt-2">The Affiliate confirms to HiTeck Education that the Affiliate is not a private individual less than 18 years of age. If you are under 18 years old and would like to become an affiliate, you must get a parent or guardian to sign-up on your behalf.</p>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">12.Applicable Law.</h2>
